VW’s Audi Plans to Produce Q3 in China, Sueddeutsche Reports

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-04-15T16:20:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-15/vw-s-audi-plans-to-produce-q3-in-china-sueddeutsche-reports.html
Volkswagen AG (VOW) ’s Audi division plans
to produce the Q3 compact sport-utility vehicle in  China ,
 Sueddeutsche Zeitung  reported, citing an interview with Chief
Executive Officer Rupert Stadler.  Producing the Q3 in China will increase the number of model
ranges made in the country to four, the newspaper quoted Stadler
as saying in a preview of an interview to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
 nkresge@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Phil Serafino at   pserafino@bloomberg.net  